title: Banshee.Origins.S01.S02.Convert.to.XviD
description:
I got the WebM files for the episodes and converted them to XviD for my own use (old hardware player). I wasted disk space in order to keep the quality as close to the original files as possible.
Just sharing them with the world for others who might need them.

Note: the titles and the numbering are correct per the *current* list at www.welcometobanshee.com.
